snippet.title: Super Mario Newest Adventure || SMBX Direct Trailer!
snippet.description:
Crazier Levels, Wackier Enemies, Lots of Challenges, and EVEN MORE!! :D


------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

"Super Mario's Shroom Shines Escapade" (Previously called "Super Mario Newest Adventure") is a Mario Fangame made with Super Mario Bros X2. 
In this brand new adventure, Mario and his fellow friends must collect the mysterious yet powerful Shroom Shines to save the Mushroom Kingdom from Bowser's army! 
(Yes, once again! What were you expecting? This ain't about Thousand Year Doors!)

Coming Soon!!
